title: MONDAY - Week 6 Recap
itunes:title: MONDAY - Week 6 Recap
description:
Week 6 in the NFL saw a matchup of two future hall of famers (0:38) in Tom Brady and Aaron Rodgers battle it out for just the third time in their illustrious careers. Nick Foles (2:56) led the Bears to a 5-1 record with the win over the Panthers, while Derrick Henry (4:02) ran wild over the Texans. We'll also have a Monday night preview (6:07) as Patrick Mahomes and the Chiefs take on Josh Allen and the Bills
